name: You Are Unlimited
description: You Are Unlimited is the first photo book by Dave Pires. After a return from the mountains to his hometown of Vancouver, BC, this project was shot entirely on film over three years, and also encompasses three coast-to-coast road trips. It is a self-published chronicle of the countless mental, emotional and geographic latitudes along the way. 76 Pages Full Colour Perfect Bound 23.8cm x 18.4cm (9.375” x 7.25”) Hand-numbered edition of 250 Preview
